OL,5,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up!
OL,6,     FEnforcement Agent Alex aims to
OL,7,     Fcollect a huge #35k debt, while
OL,8,     FMark and Sam trail a woman who
OL,9,     Fowes more than a year's worth of
OL,10,     Frent - a sizable #25k - to a
OL,11,     Fprevious landlord.
OL,12,G1800 Home and Away
OL,13,     FRichie gets it wrong. Cash
OL,14,     Fstruggles with Eden's decision.
OL,15,     FCrime escalates in Summer Bay.
OL,16,G1830 Home and Away
OL,17,     FRichie gets another shot. Jo digs
OL,18,     Fherself a deeper hole with Tane.
OL,19,     FTane's called to visit his family.
