OL,5,G2300 Skin A&E
OL,6,     FDr Dev Shah struggles to treat a
OL,7,     Ffootball fan who has a painful
OL,8,     Fball of fat below his ribcage. Dr
OL,9,     FEmma McMullen deals with a large
OL,10,     Fliquid-filled neck cyst.
OL,11,G0000 Shoplifters: Caught Red Handed
OL,12,     FUndercover detective Steve tails
OL,13,     Ftwo suspects who previously evaded
OL,14,     Fcapture, and later deals with a
OL,15,     Fwoman suspected of stealing
OL,16,     Fthousands of pounds' worth of
OL,17,     Fperfume. (Ep3)
